Help for BADWORDS:

BADWORDS maintains a list of glob strings that every word
in a channel will be checked against (if BLOCKBADWORDS is set).

The ACTION parameter can be: KICK, BAN, KICKBAN or (if your
IRCd supports it) QUIET.

Syntax: BADWORDS LIST
Syntax: BADWORDS ADD <word> <action>
Syntax: BADWORDS DEL <word>

Examples:
    /msg &nick& BADWORDS LIST
    /msg &nick& BADWORDS ADD f?ck kick
    /msg &nick& BADWORDS ADD *dam?it* quiet
    /msg &nick& BADWORDS DEL f?ck
